{"tid":1534213,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"林鄭講長期作戰你唔係信呀？佢講乜你就信乜？","createTime":"2019-09-03T02:41:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T03:47:53.000Z","uid":39092,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"242e3cbbe9f1ec97dccc2a5d820ea274db12d503","tid":1534213,"uid":39092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:41:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">777只係比你知佢想你知既野<br />\n點解要聽佢講 而忘記我地五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n條八婆只係想大家接受佢死都唔辭職呢個決定<br />\n佢而家只會全力賣港為左做大灣區區長</span></span><br />\n<br />\n成個政府根本已經急到瀨屎<br />\n假如要長期作戰，洗鬼拉咁多人<br />\n只要由得你地圍由得你地上街唔回應就得<br />\n<br />\n記住我地唔可以比政府拖住行<br />\n唔係有路線圖咩？<br />\n和理非-&gt;死線-&gt;升級-&gt;勇武-&gt;和理非"},{"pid":"be45bdf1760a1ff73bc71bf9c31d029e60c25a41","tid":1534213,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:42:00.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月8！到時見！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb8d2719f60bb740e351d299211cda198c356b96","tid":1534213,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:42:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我唔想知佢錄音內容<br />\n我推到同溫層既大家知道<br />\n你地負責幫手去fb啊等等宣傳得唔得<br />\n唔好再理膠post喇 關注返行動post<br />\n再好好運用6月至今每個核彈去twitter做文宣喇<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFJR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=7b738fca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，<br />\n請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n-大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n-高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n-高舉大量國旗<br />\n-唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼 補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n-領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"9e6476d0c6f25ff5a2fbe8adf5c7c07986913ac5","tid":1534213,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:43:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔係信777<br />\n但中共一定唔會讓步<br />\n所以最後一定變長期戰</span>"},{"pid":"008a9b17579d47551799a5ed1dc6770cb9f3cbab","tid":1534213,"uid":39092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e6476d0c6f25ff5a2fbe8adf5c7c07986913ac5","tid":1534213,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:43:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔係信777<br />\n但中共一定唔會讓步<br />\n所以最後一定變長期戰</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:44:10.000Z","msg":"中共貿易戰企硬左未呀？"},{"pid":"8378f6a4c8edce27d814075a3be62572b60fd5f8","tid":1534213,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:44:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EDe0oXbW4AEhvs_?format=png&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEDe0oXbW4AEhvs_%3Fformat%3Dpng%26name%3Dsmall&h=fbb3451c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港呢個孤兒仔<br />\n流落到谷底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e4d18b68a3407fa36b285fc673c31c59d6afa3","tid":1534213,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:44:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b3f65c68b0733db4851b40b28ced0549e22c6b1","tid":1534213,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T